 EQUB &DD, &DD, &DD, &DE, &DE, &DE, &DF, &DF
 EQUB &E0, &E0, &E0, &E1, &E1, &E1, &E2, &E2
 EQUB &E2, &E3, &E3, &E3, &E4, &E4, &E4, &E5
 EQUB &E5, &E5, &E6, &E6, &E6, &E7, &E7, &E7
